high_descs: Move to the wood dresser in the far right corner of the room
Pick up the clock on top of the dresser
Carry the clock to the left side of the dresser where the lamp is
anns.task_desc: Carry a clock while turning on a lamp

high_descs: Walk across the room to the wooden dresser next to the bed.
Pick up the leftmost silver clock off of the wooden dresser.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right to face the small lamp on the dresser.
Turn on the light of the small lamp.
anns.task_desc: Examine a silver clock in the light of a small lamp.

high_descs: Walk forward to the window on the other side of the room then turn right and walk to the dresser.
Pick up the paper weight from the dresser.
Look left out the window then look back at the dresser.
Turn on the lamp that is on the corner of the dresser.
anns.task_desc: Look at a paper weight under the light of a lamp.
